4:
FUULAN! How have you not defeated
Shuilong?! Don't tell me you've
forgotten your duties as Punisher!
6:
Shuilong has many enemies. If she
dies before we exact our revenge,
we will be the laughingstock of the
martial arts community!
9:
Forgive me... I just need more time! 
I swear, I WILL defeat Shuilong!
12:
...Any more delays, and you will be
forced to step down. I am sure there
are many who would gladly take
your place.
14:
We do not want excuses! We want
results! Defeat Shuilong by any
means necessary!
25:
No, no, no! What do I do?! If I don't
beat Shuilong soon, I won't be able
to fight her anymore!
29:
That... doesn't make sense. What do
you mean?
33:
Uhm, well, okay... I've been tasked
with getting revenge as part of my
school's credo.
35:
Only a student chosen by the
master is allowed to seek vengeance. 
Right now, that's me. But—
39:
Since you're taking too long, they're
looking at other students. 
I get it now.
44:
That's so unfair! I worked so hard for
this!
47:
Sounds like a pain in the ass. You
could just ignore 'em, right?
51:
I can't do that! The rules are the
rules, I can't break them! Besides... 
It doesn't matter how I feel.
55:
Wow. Glad I didn't join a martial arts
school.
59:
...At this point, I have no choice but
to risk everything on one final duel!
64:
Fuulan. She's not the type of person
you can beat by chance. You know
this.
68: But... but... Oh, this is hopeless!
71: ...Maybe I really should just give up.
80:
"Rules are rules"... You sure you're
okay with that?
88:
...No, I'm not. Defeating Shuilong...
That's what I care about most!
91:
My master, my classmates, and the
rules... They're important to me too,
but I can't let anyone else take this
away from me.
104:
Thanks, everyone. I think I finally
understand myself now.
111:
All right, I gotta go. I'm gonna go tell
my master and everyone else!
115:
Why bother? If you're leaving
anyway, you could just stay gone.
119:
If I'm gonna go my own way, the
least I can do is let them know.
125:
You dare disobey our credo?!
Fuulan, if this is a joke, it's not funny!
133:
I know that I'm being selfish. And I
know I owe much to everyone here.
139:
You insolent whelp! No one leaves
this place unless I say so! Get her!
142:
I won't go down without a fight. If
you're going to get in my way... 
I won't hold back!
148: What'd I say? I knew this'd happen.
152:
While I understand you have your
own codes to follow, she is our
friend. We won't stand idly by while
she's in trouble.
160:
Begone, outsiders! Our business is
none of your concern!
167: Whew! I feel so much better.
170:
Not surprising, considering how
much you cut loose back there.
174:
I finally understand now. Fighting for
some grand cause just isn't my
thing.
178:
I wanna fight because it's fun! And
that's okay with me.
182: I'm glad you've figured things out.
186:
Besides... If I'm not honest with
myself, how do I expect to ever beat
her?
190:
Watch out, Shuilong! Someday, 
I'm gonna surpass you!
202:
I'm gonna defeat you... someday,
Shuilong! I... SWEAR IT!
